The paper deals with the classification of web queries into scholar and non-scholar domains, which is a task related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of supervised learning algorithms also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), deep learning (cs.DL), and machine learning (cs.LG).
